# Basic

```elixir
Mix.install([
  {:bpf, path: ".."}
])
```

## Opening & Loading

```elixir
object = BPF.Object.open_file!("syscall_counter.o")
```

```elixir
BPF.Object.load!(object)
```

```elixir
[do_sys_enter] = object.programs
do_sys_enter
```

```elixir
[syscall_counts] = object.maps
syscall_counts
```

```elixir
link = BPF.Program.attach!(do_sys_enter)
```

```elixir
for i <- 0..256 do
  BPF.Map.lookup_elem!(syscall_counts, i)
end
```
